      "content": "honestly i was just sitting here looking out the window and it hit me how little it would actually matter if i just... wasn't here anymore. like i'm halfway across the world and i feel like a ghost. if i just disappeared tomorrow, i don't think anyone would even notice for weeks. it's weirdly peaceful thinking about how much of a zero sum game everything is.",
